    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi @Haroenv !\r\nIts still problematic with version 3.4.0. It do not give errors but the sort by is not still working fine. This widget disappears (dropdown menu) after some delay i-e 2-3 seconds. When page loads it is like this: [https://drive.google.com/file/d/16lTszOQHoNhUTPdVe63CmUmqpt-wK0G_/view?usp=sharing](dropdownPresent)\r\n\r\nAfter some time span it disappears: [https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EIGzJDuUNK9CdMZhXQccle73MXjoLRUk/view?usp=sharing](dropdownDisappears)\r\n\r\nThis was also happening previously when created this issue, but also give errors on browser's console. Now there is no error on console.\r\n\r\nI shifted to previous version of instantsearch.js by using resolutions in package.json.\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"resolutions\": {\r\n \"instantsearch.js\": \"3.4.0\",\r\n},\r\n```",
